# JavaScript Conventions

- Use **explicit boolean checks** (`if (value === true)`) rather than implicit truthy/falsy testing
- This project has no package manager or build tooling; if you see explicit need for it then ask first
- Ask before introducing JS libraries
- Use a pragmatic ES module separation for new code (see `js/mapBrowser/`, `js/registerMap/` for examples)
- Prefer clear, descriptive variable names over brevity
